session_summary: Joanna and Nate caught up at 10:55 am on 24 June, 2022. Joanna submitted her screenplay to a film contest, and Nate's gaming party was successful. Nate shared about making vegan ice cream and Joanna wanted the recipe. They agreed to share it the next day. Joanna planned to make it for her family. Nate offered support, and Joanna promised to keep him updated. Nate wished her a great day and told her to take care.

conversation_turns.speaker: Joanna
conversation_turns.text: Hey Nate, long time no see! How have you been? I just got done submitting my recent screenplay to a film contest just to see how others might like it!

conversation_turns.speaker: Nate
conversation_turns.text: That's really cool Joanna! I hope it does well, and I've been doing great! The gaming party was a great success! We even played some Chess afterward just for fun.

conversation_turns.speaker: Joanna
conversation_turns.text: Nice! Did your friends like the controller accessories?

conversation_turns.speaker: Nate
conversation_turns.text: Most of them did! I can't say if all of them will continue to use them or not, but that's beside the point.

conversation_turns.speaker: Joanna
conversation_turns.text: Yeah Nate, you're right. It doesn't matter if they use it, its the thought that matters right?

conversation_turns.speaker: Nate
conversation_turns.text: Absolutely! There were 7 people that attended, and 6 of them said they'd want to do it again next month!

conversation_turns.speaker: Joanna
conversation_turns.text: That sounds like a huge success then! Congrats!

conversation_turns.speaker: Nate
conversation_turns.blip_caption: a photography of a group of people sitting on a bench
conversation_turns.query: vegan coconut milk ice cream vegan diet group
conversation_turns.text: Thanks! On another note, I made vegan ice cream last Friday and shared it with some people in my vegan diet group. It was awesome!

conversation_turns.speaker: Joanna
conversation_turns.text: Mm, yum! Can you give me the recipe for that? It sounds like it'd be a good recipe!

conversation_turns.speaker: Nate
conversation_turns.text: Sure thing! I can give it to you tomorrow, how does that sound?

conversation_turns.speaker: Joanna
conversation_turns.text: Awesome! I'm going to make it for my family this weekend - can't wait!

conversation_turns.speaker: Nate
conversation_turns.text: Nice one, Joanna! Hope you and your family like it. Let me know how it went!

conversation_turns.speaker: Joanna
conversation_turns.text: Sure thing! They love it when I make them new things!

conversation_turns.speaker: Nate
conversation_turns.text: Then I have no doubt they'll love the icecream!

conversation_turns.speaker: Joanna
conversation_turns.text: Thanks Nate! Your support is greatly appreciated. I'll make sure to keep you updated.

conversation_turns.speaker: Nate
conversation_turns.text: Can't wait to hear about it. Have a great day! Take care.
